Essential Tools Office 2007 ControlBars
--Select the popupmenu style an right click here to see the popupmenu.--
XPMenus framework provides true context menus support. It supports various styles like OfficeXP, Office2003, VS2005, Office2007, Office2007Outlook, Metro.
It can be easily associated to a control with the help of PopupMenusManager. Popup can be cancelled from showing by handling PopupMenu's BeforePopup event.
